    section#status.half
      h2 Project status &amp; support
      p The Gitted project is relatively new. It has been used since October, 2014 on (small) production servers but {sysconf-target} has been written and {gitted} rewritten in February 2015 after some design changes.
      p {sysconf} has been {b stable} for a long time, which is not surprising given its simplicity.
